====Verb====
{{en-infl-reg-consonant|murder||}}

#{{transitive}} To [[deliberately]] [[kill]] (a person or persons).
#{{transitive}} {{sports}} {{figurative}} {{colloquial}} To [[defeat]] [[decisive]]ly.
#: ''Our team is going to murder them.''
#{{figurative}} {{colloquial}} ''Used to express one's anger at somebody.''
#: ''He's torn my best shirt.  When I see him, I'll murder him!''

=====Synonyms=====
